00:20:52,481 --> 00:20:54,061
What if I said
I don't believe you?

403
00:20:55,491 --> 00:20:58,761
Ok, you got me. I don't know
anything about wine.

404
00:21:01,641 --> 00:21:03,499
Just seems odd that
you being so willing

405
00:21:03,500 --> 00:21:05,161
